nodes.text: The High Republic: The Rising Storm (audiobook)
The High Republic: The Rising Storm is the unabridged audio version of the canon novel of the same name, written by Cavan Scott. The audiobook was released by Random House Audio on June 29, 2021.
The adventures of the Jedi of the High Republic era continue in this Star Wars novel.
